data.description: Welcome to this charming Florida home nestled in the quiet Poinciana neighborhood. An oversized corner lot with a beautifully landscaped exterior. A fully fenced yard with an enclosed patio offers privacy and ample outdoor space. Inside, this 4-bedroom, 2-bathroom residence features a spacious open floor plan with laminate and tile flooring. Cathedral ceilings lend an airy feel to the home. The gourmet kitchen is a chef's dream, equipped with stainless steel appliances, generous counter space, granite counters, storage cabinets and pantries. The spacious master bedroom includes an ensuite bath complete with a walk-in closet, tub, and a separate shower stall. Residents can take advantage of the community's fantastic amenities. Located in the heart of Poinciana Village, this property is conveniently positioned near schools, healthcare facilities, restaurants, shopping centers, and Florida's major attractions. Don't miss this opportunity to live in a comfortable and well-situated Florida home. 100% finance available , no mortgage insurance under the Community Homeownership Incentive Program.
